DataHabit project is a simple data logger for Android. Allows you to keep a personal data diary, with reminders to enter data

Key Features:
*Multiple types of data input supported:
*Comments for every data point
*Time stamps for every data point
*Scheduled reminders (hourly, daily, weekly) or multiples thereof (every 12 hours, every 3 weeks, etc.)
*Export your data via an spreadsheet (CSV) attached to an email message

URLs:
 - https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.rdpharr.DataHabit
 - http://datahabit.com
 - http://rdpharr.github.com/DataHabit/